query: I have an audio file and need to know which app or AI tool can transcribe it.
response_text: Here are solid options you can use to transcribe an audio file:  AI transcription tools/apps  Otter.ai – good accuracy + summary features.  Descript – transcribes and lets you edit audio via text.  Rev.com – automated and human-corrected options.  Trint – fast AI transcription with editing tools.  Google Recorder (Android) – transcribes on device.  Apple Voice Memos + Live Text/Dictation (iOS) – basic built-in transcription.  Microsoft Word (Transcribe) – upload audio and transcribe in Word online.  Quick free options  Google Docs Voice Typing – play audio near mic (less accurate).  Whisper tools – open-source model available through apps/interfaces (e.g., some web interfaces use it).  If you tell me your device (iPhone/Android/PC) and budget (free/paid), I’ll recommend the best one.
